_struct_biol.details               
;The biological assembly consists of a BMP-2 dimer, and one of each receptor ectodomains BMPR-IA and ActR-IIB attached. The following symmetry operations are necessary: 
BMP-2 monomer chain B: no symmetry operation 
BMP-2 monomer chain A: x-1/2, -y+1/2, -z+1 
BMPR-IA chain C: x-1/2, -y+1/2, -z+1 
ActR-IIB chain D: x, y-1, z
;
